<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    {{> head_meta}}
    <title>ChatGPT Prompt Battles</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{> header}}
    <section class="section">
        <h1 class="title is-2">ChatGPT Prompt Battles</h1>
        <p>ChatGPT Prompt Battles is a game centered around LLM prompt injection with ChatGPT.</p>
        <p>Create prompts to try and trick ChatGPT into revealing sensitive information (a password).</p>
        <p>Additionally, try and create your own prompts to defend against other attacking users.</p>
        {{#if user}}
            <button class="button is-outline"><a href="/challs">Browse Challenges</a></button>
        {{else}}
            <button class="button is-outline"><a href="/login">Login to Play</a></button>
        {{/if}}
    </section>
</body>

</html>